{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"case","externalID":"s:3GIO18FileIconSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","title":"FileIconSignalName.notify"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/fileiconsignalname\/notify"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileIconSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileIconSignalName"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/FileIconSignalName/notify":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileIconSignalName\/notify","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"title":"FileIconSignalName.notify","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/fileiconsignalname\/notify","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/FileIconSignalName":{"title":"FileIconSignalName","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileIconSignalName","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FileIconSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/fileiconsignalname","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"FileIconSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"title":"canonical parameter names","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"canonical parameter names"}],"url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"}}}